<tib. 1.6.82> Conmemorant merito tot mala ferre senem,
<tib. 1.6.83> Hanc Venus exalto flentem sublimis Olympo
<tib. 1.6.84> Spectat et, infidis quam sit acerba, monet.
<tib. 1.6.85> Haec aliis maledicta cadant; nos, Delia, amoris
